data.description: Great 4 sided brick home on quiet street overlooking the large, partially fenced yard. Inside features open living areas with separate dining room, large eat in kitchen and laundry/utility room. 3 good sized bedrooms, master has ensuite bath. An additional bath makes up the main floor. Downstairs, the basement has been finished, with brick fireplace and large living/game area, as well as room for an additional bath. Also, there is a separate, spacious shop area with workbench, and garage door leading to outside, great for storing lawn equipment. This is an amazing home with enormous potential! Seller is giving a $5,000 carpet/paint allowance!
